  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60d87bc7b42a64001c66a409",
      "text": "美文章",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800202,
      "updated": 1624800391
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87bea1280f00000814091",
      "text": "長く美しい[文章]のこと",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800234,
      "updated": 1624800282
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87bea1280f00000814092",
      "text": " ……っと書いても曖昧すぎて[/icons/わからん.icon]だろうから、もっと具体的に書きたい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800235,
      "updated": 1624800307
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c341280f00000814096",
      "text": " scrapbox系の話題だと、[箇条書き]の対比語として使われることがある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800307,
      "updated": 1624800348
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c1a1280f00000814093",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800282,
      "updated": 1624800282
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c5d1280f00000814098",
      "text": "具体例",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800349,
      "updated": 1624800351
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87f4e1280f000008140ac",
      "text": " [文体]も重視される文章",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624801102,
      "updated": 1624801125
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87f6d1280f000008140ad",
      "text": "  中身だけでなく文の[巧緻さ]も大事になる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624801133,
      "updated": 1624801153
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87f831280f000008140b1",
      "text": "   [/ikiwiki/美文章滅させない]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624801155,
      "updated": 1624801155
    },
    {
      "id": "6357bd9c5e90c0000057b573",
      "text": "   [レトリック]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666694557,
      "updated": 1666694632
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c5f1280f00000814099",
      "text": "  小説の文体",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800351,
      "updated": 1624801130
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c631280f0000081409a",
      "text": "  随筆の文体",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800355,
      "updated": 1624801126
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c661280f0000081409b",
      "text": "  プロモーションテキスト",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800358,
      "updated": 1624801127
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87ca51280f000008140a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800421,
      "updated": 1624800421
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87caa1280f000008140a4",
      "text": "美文章でも箇条書きでもない文章",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800425,
      "updated": 1624800432
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87cb01280f000008140a5",
      "text": " [論文]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800432,
      "updated": 1624800435
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87cb31280f000008140a6",
      "text": "  主張→根拠→結論というformatに統一されている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800435,
      "updated": 1624800461
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87ccd1280f000008140a7",
      "text": "  場合によっては言い回しできれいに見せかけている論文もあるかもしれない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800461,
      "updated": 1624800480
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87c9c1280f0000081409f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800412,
      "updated": 1624800412
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87be21280f00000814090",
      "text": "Reference",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800226,
      "updated": 1624800228
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87bca1280f0000081408e",
      "text": " [/shokai/美文章滅すべし]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800202,
      "updated": 1624800418
    },
    {
      "id": "60d87bcb1280f0000081408f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1624800202,
      "updated": 1624800202
    },
    {
      "id": "612a729a1280f000005f08ca",
      "text": "[長く美しい文章]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1630171802,
      "updated": 1630171809
    },
    {
      "id": "612a72a11280f000005f08cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1630171809,
      "updated": 1630171809
    },
    {
      "id": "613069308ee92a0000cffaca",
      "text": "何故「長い」という形容詞が入るのだろう? [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630562609,
      "updated": 1630562620
    },
    {
      "id": "613069338ee92a0000cffacb",
      "text": " 美文かどうかと長さは関係なくないですか",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630562611,
      "updated": 1630562653
    },
    {
      "id": "61306f6e1280f00000233eae",
      "text": "  [/shokai/美文章滅すべし]で使われていた[\" 長く美しい文章]をそのまま用いただけですが、確かに「美しい文章」だけでも十分かもしれませんね[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1630564207,
      "updated": 1630564253
    },
    {
      "id": "6130694d8ee92a0000cffacc",
      "text": "  「美しい文章」は大抵長ったらしいからだろうか？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1630562638,
      "updated": 1630564281
    },
    {
      "id": "61307b7f8ee92a0000cffacd",
      "text": "  そんなことはないのでは? [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630567295,
      "updated": 1630567303
    },
    {
      "id": "64999c29b8bbfc0000a62f3b",
      "text": " 確かに美しさと簡潔さはトレードオフとは限らないこともある[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1687788585,
      "updated": 1687788787
    },
    {
      "id": "64999ce1b8bbfc0000a62f3c",
      "text": " \t最大限に短く美しい文章が書けたらいいなあと思う[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1687788769,
      "updated": 1687788799
    },
    {
      "id": "6698f55771b3c20000aa6576",
      "text": " \t\t[短歌][who.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1721300246,
      "updated": 1721300256
    },
    {
      "id": "61306f4e1280f00000233ead",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1630564174,
      "updated": 1630564174
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a5055e90c00000b5ff51",
      "text": "[美しい][文章]ってどんなのがあるのかな[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965061,
      "updated": 1669965209
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a5995e90c00000b5ff54",
      "text": "　多分に人の好みが関わる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965209,
      "updated": 1669965224
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a5b25e90c00000b5ff55",
      "text": "　人に意見を聞いたり、Wikiに書くときには避けたほうがよいらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965235,
      "updated": 1669965335
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a5f85e90c00000b5ff56",
      "text": "　　理由は美文書滅すべしに書いてある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965304,
      "updated": 1669965325
    },
    {
      "id": "669850534fc3250000a40c45",
      "text": "　内容が美しい[Yupbox.icon]",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258067,
      "updated": 1721258235
    },
    {
      "id": "6698505c4fc3250000a40c46",
      "text": "　英語を日本語訳した本にたまに美しい文章と感じる[Yupbox.icon]",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258077,
      "updated": 1721258237
    },
    {
      "id": "669850b74fc3250000c03ec9",
      "text": "　　たいてい一文がやたら長い",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258168,
      "updated": 1721258177
    },
    {
      "id": "669850a84fc3250000c03ec8",
      "text": "　　構造の美しさなのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258152,
      "updated": 1721258164
    },
    {
      "id": "6698507a4fc3250000a40c47",
      "text": "　　他の言語の日本語訳でも感じるのかな、わからない",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258106,
      "updated": 1721258150
    },
    {
      "id": "669851164fc3250000c03eca",
      "text": "　本を読んでいて美しい文章だと感じることがあっても、SNSやチャットなどのコミュニケーションの文章で感じた事は無い[Yupbox.icon]",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258262,
      "updated": 1721258395
    },
    {
      "id": "669851544fc3250000c03ecb",
      "text": "　　なぜだろう",
      "userId": "6662d4b8f251da001c4fc325",
      "created": 1721258324,
      "updated": 1721258330
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a5165e90c00000b5ff53",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965078,
      "updated": 1669965078
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b0565b98c200001a9bb9",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967958,
      "updated": 1669967961
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b0595b98c200001a9bba",
      "text": " [美文]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967961,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bbb",
      "text": "  たぶん、[違う概念]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669968027
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bbc",
      "text": " [名文]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bbd",
      "text": "  たぶん、違う概念",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bbe",
      "text": "  [名文家]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bbf",
      "text": "　[美辞麗句]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc0",
      "text": "　 たぶん近い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b27b5e90c00000b5ff58",
      "text": "　 なるほど！[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669968507,
      "updated": 1669968511
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc1",
      "text": " [巧言令色]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc2",
      "text": "  たぶんこれも近い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669968014
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc3",
      "text": " [ポエム]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc4",
      "text": " [エッセイ]、[随筆]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6389b07e5b98c200001a9bc5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1669967998,
      "updated": 1669967998
    },
    {
      "id": "6698cd76be12ad0000f50ba9",
      "text": "[sume.icon]",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1721290103,
      "updated": 1721290104
    },
    {
      "id": "6698cde3be12ad0000f50bbe",
      "text": " [簡而盡，直而不肆]",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1721290212,
      "updated": 1721290216
    },
    {
      "id": "6698cd77be12ad0000f50baa",
      "text": " 　[出師表]",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1721290104,
      "updated": 1721290213
    },
    {
      "id": "6698cde9be12ad0000f50bbf",
      "text": " 　個人の好みの要素が大きいとおもう",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1721290218,
      "updated": 1721290456
    },
    {
      "id": "6389a50c5e90c00000b5ff52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669965068,
      "updated": 1669965068
    }
  ]
}